::KitKat::

She pulled back and looked into drillbit's eyes. "We need to get 
everyone ready.  In the next hour or two, Megatron and his forces 
will be here.  Along with Aracnia's. We need to get everything ready 
to greet them, then we attach the Allince base.  Please, gather 
everyone up and tell them to get ready.  IN two hours, we attack."
